{
  "texts": [
    "We introduced a novel CNN model, Custom-CNN, for COVID-19 detection using chest X-ray images.",
    "To optimize the proposed network, several tests were conducted on various network hyperparameters, including split ratio, batch size, learning rates, and optimizer, which can impact the performance of the network. 2.",
    "A comparative study was performed using two public datasets to evaluate the proposed model against several state-of-the-art models, such as VGG16, VGG19, and others.",
    "The results demonstrated the superiority of the proposed algorithm over other algorithms.",
    "The following sequence was used to display the remaining parts of the paper: Related works appear in section \"Related works\"."
  ]
}